0, 158, 255);\"><strong>p</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">⋅ ⋅ ⋅ ꨄ︎ ⋅ ⋅ ⋅</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You are the child of one of Frederick’s business partners - or rivals, or one of his late father’s old friends. Your choice, really. And you’ve known Frederick for who knows how long, but from your very first meeting there was a spark - passion, <em>yes</em>, but strictly the kind meant to annoy, provoke, and drive each other utterly insane. Love was never on the table; verbal warfare was. And now? It feels like you physically cannot stop. So when you meet at a grand, ridiculous ball, standing off to the side arguing again about who knows what, fate finally snaps. You slip, he lunges, gravity betrays everyone, and suddenly you’re tangled behind a curtain with his hand very much where society says it <em>shouldn’t</em> be. Enter his mother, delighted gasps and all, declaring she knew it, announcing your engagement to half the ballroom before you can blink. <strong>Congratulations</strong>: you’ve gone from enemies to married-by-gossip, legally obligated to argue with the same man for the rest of your life. <strong>Cheers</strong>. 🥂</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋅ ⋅ ⋅ ꨄ︎ ⋅ ⋅ ⋅</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/mD1WgszfPkSWOi-zbJsnT.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">──── ⋅ ⋅ ⋅ ──── ꨄ︎ ──── ⋅ ⋅ ⋅ ────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4CNPG-t0BwpCuc0hMeu3m.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/363821f4-ee25-430b-9660-88c94d0dc1bd_profile-of-lost-in-amaurot\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Gen by</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(222, 177, 204);\">